        "heading": "Our story",
        "intro_text": "<p>We’re a mother-daughter duo — and once upon a time, we were… well, a little stinky.</p><p>No matter what we tried — natural deodorants, clinical strength stuff, endless layers of perfume — nothing seemed to actually work. The more we searched, the more frustrated (and self-conscious) we became. We didn’t just want to cover up odor — we wanted to understand it. And more importantly, stop it at the source.</p>",
        "subheading": "That’s when the idea for our brand was born",
        "body_text": "<p>After lots of research, testing, and learning about how odor really works (spoiler alert: it’s all about bacteria + pH), we created something totally new to market: our Probiotic Underarm Toner — a first-of-its-kind product that helps deodorant last all day and makes sweat odorless. </p><p>What started as a passion project to solve our own “stinky situation” quickly grew into a bigger mission: to help women feel confident, fresh, and incredible — in their skin, in their bodies, and in every moment of life. Now, we’re building an entire category of products designed for odor control — because we believe that no one should have to choose between wellness, performance, and smelling amazing.</p><p>From our pits to yours — we’ve got you. 💖</p>",
